{"word":"G526 - ἀπαλλοτριόω - apallotrióō - ap-al-lot-ree-o'-o - Alienate","slug":"G526","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπαλλοτριόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>apallotrióō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ap-al-lot-ree-o'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Alienate"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03C0;&#x03B1;&#x03BB;&#x03BB;&#x03BF;&#x03C4;&#x03C1;&#x03B9;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - apallotrioo&#x0304;</b> - <i>ap-al-lot-ree-o'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G575\">G575</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G245\">G245</a>; to <i>estrange away</i>, that is, (passively and figuratively) to <i>be non participant:</i> - alienate, be alien."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G241\">G241</a>, <a href=\"#/G243\">G243</a>, <a href=\"#/G245\">G245</a>, <a href=\"#/G246\">G246</a>"}]}